'''布拉索沃区'''（{{lang-ru|Брасовский район}}）是[[俄罗斯联邦|俄罗斯联邦]][[布良斯克州|布良斯克州]]下辖的一个[[区_(苏联)|区]]，其行政中心为[[洛科季_(布良斯克州)|洛科季]]<ref name="I͡Uferev1992">{{cite book|author=Oleg Vasilʹevich I͡Uferev|title=Business-map Russia: Russia, the Central Region|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fuciAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA41|year=1992|publisher=MP "NIK"|isbn=978-5-87484-003-7|pages=41–45|access-date=2020-11-27|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204154907/https://books.google.com/books?id=fuciAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA41}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title=21世纪世界地名录 中英文本|last=萧德荣，周定国主编|first=|publisher=北京：现代出版社|year=2001.02|isbn=7-80028-595-2|location=|pages=378}}</ref>。据2016年统计，该区的人口为20078人。<ref name=stat>{{ cite web |url=http://bryansk.gks.ru/wps/wcm/connect/rosstat_ts/bryansk/resources/5ba68a8047169cd3b972b987789c42f5/Nas-2016.htm |title=Оценка численности населения Брянской области по городским округам и муниципальным районам на 1 января 2016 года |accessdate=2016-04-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6gl1URp6z?url=http://bryansk.gks.ru/wps/wcm/connect/rosstat_ts/bryansk/resources/5ba68a8047169cd3b972b987789c42f5/Nas-2016.htm |archivedate=2016-04-14 |language=ru |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

